template.description: Capture Web Socket Attributes and Message
template.name: WebSocketDataFlow

config.comments: get session id from attribute and not content '${websocket.session.id}' as session_id,

entry.value: SELECT '${websocket.session.id}' as session_id, msg as text_message FROM FLOWFILE

config.comments: Convert Attributes Name to match final table column using sql alias

entry.value: SELECT "websocket.local.address" as local_address, "websocket.session.id" as session_id, "websocket.remote.address" as remote_address, "websocket.endpoint.id" as endpoint_id FROM FLOWFILE
